snippet.title: Monster Energy Supercross - The Official Videogame 3 | 7deucedeuce Adam Enticknap - Be One of Us
snippet.description:
More than just a song, more than just a music video. Adam Enticknap found the funniest way to #BeOneOfUs! Take a look at this video clip. We're sure you can't stop singing.

How bad do you really wanna be the one
Do you got what it takes to be the champion
Can you be the best 
Can you beat the best
Well gear it up, and put it on the podium
 
We brought an all new compound, co-op
line it up, or freeride with some friends
We built you every single test track
(what)
Practice where the pros do the motos never end
New dedicated servers crispy like my 450
You can keep on winning even if they always quitting 
 
*Whatchu waitin’ for (what are you waiting for), get to racin, time is tickin’
*If you wanna be the best, then you gotta live it
 
Be one of us 
you could be one of us
Be one of us 
you could be one of us
Be one of us 
you could be one of us
Be one of us 
you could be one of us
 
Let’s go 
hop up on the controls
Track editor is back,
make it your own
Build it your way,
Jumps to the bleachers
We added sand,
And some sick new features
It’s time now,
That you step up to the big show,
Where the lights are
And the best glow
Is it your time
Then don’t waste 
Pick your team 
Let’s go raaaaccceeeee
 
How bad do you really wanna be the one
Do you got what it takes to be the champion
Can you be the best 
Can you beat the best
Well gear up, and put it on the podium
